            <p>On second review, this functionality already exists (albeit in a slightly roundabout way).  Both Row and Rowset supply a {{getTable()}} method, so this is possible:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$columns = $row-&gt;getTable()-&gt;info('cols');
</code></pre>

<p>I don't see any real added value to providing a {{getColumns}} wrapper around this at this late stage in ZFv1's lifecycle.  If anyone disagrees, please feel free to reopen the issue.</p>

